  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Allalin is on half board.</p>
<p>Fuel up for the day at the excellent buffet breakfast with a variety of hot and cold items. When you return from skiing, enjoy a complimentary afternoon tea buffet which includes a pastries and other sweet treats. Drinks are not included. </p>
<p>Each evening a five course evening meal including a salad buffet and choice of main course is served in the R<span>estaurant Walliserkann. Early meals for children are available from 6:30pm.</span></p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
