<li>Safe</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Seating area</li>
<li>Desk</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathroom with bath or shower</li>
<li>All rooms can accommodate a cot</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
